focal_method.body:
static String getHeaderLine() {
    String[] fields = {"DatabaseID",
      "DiseaseName",
      "Qualifier",
      "HPO_ID",
      "Reference",
      "Evidence",
      "Onset",
      "Frequency",
      "Sex",
      "Modifier",
      "Aspect",
      "Biocuration"};
    return "#" + String.join("\t", fields);
  }
